publishedStory:
Fat Macdonald had a shoe
E-I-E-I-O
And on that turd he had a bird
E-I-E-I-O
With a quack quack here
And a quack quack there
Here a quack, there a quack
Everywhere a quack quack
Fat Macdonald had a shoe
E-I-E-I-O.
Why did the ant named Andy jump the smelly pool? To fly to the other dark slime!
